pan></span></span></p>
<h3 id=3D"user-content-skhd-1" node=3D"[object Object]">skhd<a class=3D"xlo=
g-anchor" tabindex=3D"-1" href=3D"https://xlog.pseudoyu.com/macos_window_ma=
nagement_solution_using_yabai_and_skhd.md#user-content-skhd-1">#</a></h3>
<p>After configuring yabai, we have achieved intelligent split-screen, but =
sometimes the window positions provided by the algorithm do not meet our ne=
eds, or we need to frequently switch/adjust between various windows. In tha=
