<p>Additionally, there is a small setting I like: open <strong>System Prefe=
rences - Accessibility - Display - Display - Reduce Motion</strong>. This w=
ill reduce the animation effects when switching between different desktops,=
 improving switching speed. Combined with our automatic split-screen and sh=
ortcuts, it achieves fast and powerful multi-workspace switching. I priorit=
ize speed and efficiency, so those who enjoy macOS animations can skip this=
 setting.</p>
